ygData.messageBody:
I'm so covered in crap it's painful to describe.

Brigandine Tunic (Green and Silver on wood elves)
Lambent Arms
Lambent Bracers
Iksar Scaled Gloves (Silly silver pad on the backs of my hands
Shin Greaves (Icky pinkish silver)
Bronze Boots (Ugh, orange feetsies)
Skull Shaped Barbute (Silver with Gold Triangle)

Brrr, I get shivers just thinking about how crappy I look right now.

Kit


Wow Kit, now that's ugly!

I've got:
Lumberjack cap (brown)
Dwarven tunic (silver with green)
lambent sleeves (blue)
?? bracer (silver)
?? gloves (black)
lambent pants (blue)
ringmail boots (sorta brownish greenish grey)

Not a bad look, really. But every now and then I run into the friend who
gave me bronze boots and bracers and she asks why I'm not wearing them.
"Too much weight" I lie. ;^)

Peace
Evulia, twinked, but only because my guildmates won't take no for an
answer, Tunare
